  "steps": [
    "Weigh out the CsCl M = 8 (p25-1) MW = 168.37 Grams of CsCl to be added to Buffer %s %s p M 25 mls 50 mls 75 mls 100 mls 200 mls 1.3 2.4 10.10 20.20 30.31 40.41 80.82 1.4 3.2 13.47 26.94 44.16 53.86 107.76 1.45 3.6 30.24 60.48 1.5 4 16.87 33.74 50.61 67.48 1.55 4.4 18.48 36.96 73.92 1.6 4.8 20.2 40.40 1.65 5.2 21.89 43.78 87.55 1.7 5.6 23.57 47.15 70.7 94.29",
    "Add a little Mg2+ (high in Mg2+) buffer with stir bar.",
    "Add CsCl slowly until all the CsCl is dissolved",
    "Bring up the volume, rinse the stir bar.",
    "Add 50 mM Tris pH 7.6",
    "Add 100 mM MgCl 2"
